                "arguments": [],
                "code": "while #menuStack > 0 do\n  table.remove(menuStack)\n  table.remove(inputStack)\nend\nscreen:setScreen(nil)\ndecor:setScreen(message)\nselectedMessage = math.random(1,11)\nmessageText1:setValue(messages1[selectedMessage])\nmessageText2:setValue(messages2[selectedMessage])\nmessageText3:setValue(messages3[selectedMessage])\ninput:setInputHandler(interruptHandler)\nmessageTimer:setTime(0)\nmessageTimer:play()"
